@node "SAINT DRAGON"
SAINT DRAGON

Type "CAPS DECAFFEINATED" then 'Return' for infinite lives.
"CAPS WEAPON0,LEVEL0,LIVES0" to increase it.

Not sure what the following cheats do but try them.  During play press the
'Cap Lock' key, then type the phrase (including spaces) and press the 'Return'
key and the 'Caps Lock' key to turn it off.

    "I HATE THE RADION ADVENT"
    "SOMETHING SPOCK BUILT"
    "THE GNOME AT HOME"            (From Amiga Power magazine)
    "WE LOVE THE PUNTENTAY"
@endnode
@node "SARAKON"
SARAKON

Passwords are: LUNKWILL and VRANX
@endnode
@node "SATAN"
SATAN

Hold down the 'ALT', '1' and 'D' keys as the warrior during game one and
you'll receive infinite lives.  Hold down the 'ALT', '1' and 'M' keys as
the wizard  during game two for infinite lives and credits.
@endnode
@node "SAVAGE"
SAVAGE

Right at the beginning of the game (blue sector) you will find a well on the
left.  Run towards it and jump before you hit the wall.  Now you will find
yourself at the other side of it.  Keep on walking to the left and you will
notice the screen going crazy.   Waggle the joystick in all directions and
after a while you will find yourself in the red sector.  Once in the red
sector do the same as in the blue sector.  Now you go to the purple sector.
Do the same as in the red and blue sectors.  A message appears that you have
completed game one and the code word for game two.

The password for levels:

            2: SABATTA.
            3: PORSCHE
   Last level: FERGUS

For infinite lives enter "BRUISER" on the title screen on part two.

When level three is loaded, select the enter code for level two option on the
menu and when prompted enter "PORSCHE".  Right at the beginning of the game
(blue sector) you will find a well on the left.  Run towards it and jump
before you hit the wall.  Now you will find yourself at the other side of it.
Keep on walking to the left and you will notice the screen going crazy.
Waggle the joystick in all directions and after a while you will find
yourself in the red sector.  Once in the red sector do the same as in the
blue sector.  Now you go to the purple sector.  Do the same as in the red and
blue sectors.  A message appears that you have completed game one and the
code word for game two.
@endnode
@node "SCI"
SCI

On the title screen, type "IN A GARDEN IN".  During play, press 'T' for more
time.
@endnode
@node "SCOOBY & SCRAPPY DOO"
SCOOBY & SCRAPPY DOO

Typing the following with no capitals will give you continues up to Iceland:
"qwertyuiopasdfghjklzxcvbnm" (that's all the keyboard letters).
@endnode
@node "SCORPION"
SCORPION

Get a high score, type "IMPORTLIGAT" for ten lives.  Try also typing in "CRL"
and "CLEMENT" for odd fx.
@endnode
@node "SDI (Activision)"
SDI (Activision)

Shoot down all the swirling pods, then on the high score table type in
 ALERIC".  This cheat is activated and you can use the functions keys to
select any level that you wish.  
@endnode
@node "S.D.I. (Cinemaware)"
S.D.I. (Cinemaware)

When you're in the Russian space station, pick one man and keep firing at him
10 to 15 times.  No other men will appear and you can keep doing it until you
get the girl.
@endnode
