@node "SEVEN GATES OF JAMBALA"
SEVEN GATES OF JAMBALA

This is not the simplest of cheat modes.  On the title screen type (with
spaces) "YICKE YACKE H[HNERKACKE" hold down the left shift button, hold down
'1', release '1', release left shift.  The title should turn to blue.  Go to
the game.  Keys '1' - '7' take you to the levels, 'F1' - 'F5' select weapons
and 'G' to give you gold.  Check out the other function buttons too...
@endnode
@node "SHADOW DANCER"
SHADOW DANCER

Pause the game, type "GIVE ME INFINITES" followed by the 'Return' key, then
unpause the game.  Press 'X' key to skip levels.
@endnode
@node "SHADOW OF THE BEAST"
SHADOW OF THE BEAST

When the "beast" title appears, hold down both mouse buttons and the joystick
button until asked to insert disk 2.  This will give you unlimited lives.
Unfortunately, this does not work on all versions.
@endnode
@node "SHADOW OF BEAST II"
SHADOW OF BEAST II

Start playing the game.  Go to the right until you get to the forest, where
the warrior says to you, "DO NOT ENTER THESE WOODS".  Press 'A' (for Ask),
then type "TEN PINTS".  Then it will say "THIS ONE IS FOR YOU ROGER.
CHEAT MODE ACTIVATED."  Don't get killed or this will not activate infinite
lives.


     Level Passwords

     Level 1 - Eternity
     Level 2 - Sunstone
     Level 3 - Necropolis

Also, try these words in the game:  MALETO, KARAM, PIGM, PYGM, SEA,
                                    OLD, MAN, COMPA, SACK, PACK, GATE
                                    
                               ( GAME HINTS)

Go left to where the bad guy has a guy trapped in a force field.  Quickly hit
the bad guy a couple of times to kill him and free the lower guy, who will
then tell you the position of a switch (upper or lower) for use later in the
game.  Now go left and down the rope to the swamp.  Go left until you get to
the building.  Enter the building, go left and pick up the jug.  Now go back
to where you started the game.  From here go right and through the spear
throwing dudes.  Go up and kill the guy who is throwing the green puddle
things at you.  Pick up the axe he drops.  Now go left and fall from the
ledge.  Go right to the rock that is by itself and you can see a little
grassy spot on the ground.  Jump on this some 4 - 5 times and it will fall
through.  Go down the steps and you are in the crystal cavern.  Go left, at
the bridge a guy will start running left.  Chase him and he will take you to
a bridge that is being mechanically shortened.  Jump and shoot the dude
that's cranking the bridge (3 or so shots with the axe).  Now break the door
at the other side of the bridge with your ball & chain.  Go up the first
chandelier.  Go left and hit the correct switch.  Now go down and kill the
guards and go right.  Get the key and go left.  You will get caught and they
will throw you in jail.  USE THE 'O' command and give the jug to the guard.
After he passes out, break down the door with the ball & chain.  Kill the
guard.  Go up the rope (faster than the prisoner) and kill the guard at the
upper left.  Then go back down the rope to get the key he dropped.  Now go up
the rope and go left at the first chance you get.  Use one of the keys and
free the prisoner.  Go to the top of the rope and then left to get the ring.
Now if you go right, the prisoners get killed.  Give the ring to the old man
who lost it, but he'll still want a parchment before he'll teach you a spell.
The other key is for the locked door in the first building (i.e. the inn
where you got the jug).                                  
@endnode
@node "SHADOW OF BEAST III"
SHADOW OF BEAST III

On the title screen, type "DADDY DRAW THIS FOR ME" and press 'RETURN'.  The
shurikan should turn to a smiley face with letters under it.  During the
game, use the 'RIGHT CURSOR' key for invicibility and the 'LEFT CURSOR' key
to return to normal.
@endnode
@node "SHADOW WARRIORS"
SHADOW WARRIORS

During intro screen press 'CTRL', 'ESC', 'F2', '5', 'V', 'J', 'Right Alt',
'Help', 'Left bracket' & 'Enter' on numeric pad (may require a friend to help
press all the keys together).   Now when the title screen plays, the bottom
of the screen will flash to indicate that the cheat is activated.  During
play the 'Help' keys skips levels.  The 'Q' key turns off the collision
detection, and the '1' and '2' keys give more energy for player 1 and player
2, respectively. 

Another cheat:

When you reach the continue option screen and, if after the word credit, it
says "1", start tapping the '1' and '2' keys alternately, all the way through
the change disk prompt until both men fall from the sky.  This gives you
infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "SHINOBI"
SHINOBI

When the "Shinobi" logo appears on the title screen, hold down the letter 'T'
and move the mouse to control it.

Pause the game during play and type:

   LARSVii for unlimited credits.
   LARSVii while holding down left mouse button to enter colour mode (this
           is controlled with numeric pad)
   Pressing 'Q' while the game is paused, lets you enter music mode.

If you have another life left, when you get to the helicopter boss, pause the
game and type: "HELICOPTERTOOTOUGHFORME".  Then die and you will go to level
3.
@endnode
@node "SHOCKWAVE"
SHOCKWAVE

A few hints and tips follow, on how each of the four zones (armys, factories,
mines and rigs) affect the game:

MINES -    Each time a mine is purchased, the income you receive for each
           time pass doubles.
FACTORYS - The more factories you have, the faster more weapons are produced.
           These are essential.
RIGS -     These supply you with the fuel for each mission run.  The more
           rigs you have the, greater the amount of fuel you receive for each
           time pass.
ARMYS -    For every army unit you own, the enemy slows down, eg. you have
           one army unit, for each four time passes that occur the enemy
           won't move for one time pass.  If more than 50% of the sector is
           occupied by the enemy, then you will lose one of your assests for
           each time pass that occurs.  The best solution is that when 30% of
           the sector is occupied, go attack the enemy.
@endnode        
@node "SIDEARMS"
SIDEARMS

While playing, hit 'CAPS LOCK', and type in "FTBOK".  You may now use the
following keys:

 '1-5' - Weapon select.
 '6' -   Faster speed.  
 '7' -   Slower speed.
 '8' -   Lives.
 '9' -   Beta suit.
 'C' -   Clear last enemy of stage.   
 'D' -   Screen dump/die.   
 'H' -   ????? 
 'I' -   Menu.
 'J' - Joystick
 'K' -   Kill off enemy.
 'L' -   Add 100k to score.
 'M' - Mouse
 'P' - Pause
 'Q' -   Quit to desktop.
 'R' -   Restart.
 'T' -   Game stats.
 'X AND 0-9' - Set stage. 
@endnode
@node "SIDEWINDER"
SIDEWINDER

If you look on disk 2, you will see a screen editor program.  You can access
a specific level by pressing the appropriate function key.  You can save the
changes by holding down both mouse buttons.  You should back up disk 2 first,
since the changes are permanent.
@endnode
@node "SILKWORM"
SILKWORM

Type "SCRAP 28" on the control option screen for infinite lives.

Version 1: Hold down the 'HELP' key and keep it pressed while pressing fire
and you'll get infinite lives and can move thru the levels by pressing the
numeric keys '1' to '0' and the minus key.

Version 2: If you have the latest version, then attempting the above will
reveal the message: "Congratulations!, you have found the cheat mode...
unfortunately it has been ZZAPPED!".  If this happens, goto the control
selection and type "scrap 28" and then start the game.  The effect is the
same as above.
@endnode
@node "SIM CITY"
SIM CITY

Press and hold 'SHIFT' and type "FUND" for $10,000.  It will cause an
earthquake every tenth time you do it, so do it before you start your city.

Another tip is to set the citizen's taxes to 0%.  Then just before tax
collection (December or November if playing at fast speed) quickly set the
taxes up to 20%.  Then after you collect taxes, put it back down to 0%.  This
way the citizens think they are not paying any taxes.

You can build land on water.  Find a straight (horizontal or vertical),
stretch of coastline and string a powerline along it.  Next, move one square
over, out into the water and string another powerline parallel to the first.
Repeat as many times as you want.  Then just bulldoze all the excess
powerlines and you can build on the new land.  

To MAKE land you simply make a 3 lane highway across any water source.
When you make a road by putting 3 sections of road on top of three section
of road on top of three sections of road (3 by 3) you make 1 section of
land in the middle.                WWWWW   WWWWW     To make more land, just
                                   WRRRW   WRRRW     move you roads over, or
           L= land                 WRRRW = WRLRW     make your roads 4 by 4,
           W= water                WRRRW   WRRRW     5 by 5 etc.  Play with
           R= road                LLRRRLL LLRRRLLL   it.  It'll work.
                                  LLLLLLL LLLLLLLL

@endnode
@node "SIMPSONS"
SIMPSONS

Try typing "COWABUNGA" to make the game easier.  Type "EAT MY SHORTS" to skip
through the different levels.  Type "SHEEP IN A GROUP WEARING HATS" to earn
infinite lives.

When you have the whistle, stand by the last window of the Springfield
Retirement Home and blow it.  Now a guy should appear and start throwing
lotsa money at you, so grab it and go on a shopping spree!
@endnode
@node "SIMULCRA"
SIMULCRA

 THE MOTHERSHIP: It follows you around generating meanies and can take many
 hits.  Ram rather than shoot.

 HOMING WEAPONS: Retreat as fast as possible then shot them.  Most homing
 weapons have a limited range and can be out run.

 BLITZKRIEG: The best attack is a fast one.  Attack a generator by flying
 along power barriers at full speed.  Learn to recognise the edge barriers.
 Barriers you can shut down never merge with the edge, and nearly always lead
 to a generator.
@endnode
@node "SINBAD & THRONE OF FALCON"
SINBAD & THRONE OF FALCON

When you are about to die, select the close icon, and then continue.  You'll
be as good as new and back at the map.
@endnode
