@node "SKIDZ"
SKIDZ

Start the game as usual and hold down the firebutton, 'ALT' and 'C' together
for infinite lives.  'M' key will skip levels.

Hold down the firebutton, 'ALT' and 'M' (one source says it's the 'L' key)
for access to any level any time.  Don't activate both or you won't get past
level two.
@endnode
@node "SKY HIGH STUNTMAN"
SKY HIGH STUNTMAN

Simply type "CHEAT" on the title screen to give you infinite lives and smart
bombs.
@endnode
@node "SLAYER"
SLAYER

Make your way to end of the first stage ensuring you're on your last life.
Blow up all of the enemy guns and the little green monster.  Next, crash into
the machine it resided in.  You will then start on level 2 with infinite
lives.

Another cheat says:

Confront the end-of-level guardian with one life intact.  Press 'D', then
crash into its dead body.  You'll now have infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "SLEEPWALKER"
SLEEPWALKER

When on the title screen, type in "DINGADINGDANGMYDANGALONGLINGLONG" and
Ralph's red nose will turn bright green.  Now when the game starts, just
press enter to skip levels.  Tab will top up Lee's sleep bar, and give you
nine attempts and light up the word COMIC.  Finally, tapping 'M' will give
you a full level map.

To find `COMIC`:
 C is above the shop canopy and to the left of the nite club.
 O is past the bouncer.
 M is past the sewer water to the left.
 I is up and to the left past the telegraph cable above the car.
 C is along the top right of the map.

Secret Message:
Pick up the beard near the first "C".  Go to th sewer exit near the traffic
lights and hit the four arrows.  Go through the sewer to the right.
@endnode
