@node "SPACE CRUSADE"
SPACE CRUSADE

Choose your team, then press the corresponding key on the key pad.  With 1
being the team on the left; 2 the middle team; and 3 the team on the right.
Keep the key pressed down and move the pointer under the door and click the
LEFT BUTTON four times, then the RIGHT BUTTON four times.  The border should
flash to let you know that it worked.   While being attacked, press the 'ESC'
key repeatedly.  This will reduce the attackers' score and inflict less
damage on your soldiers.
@endnode
