@node "SPIDERMAN"
SPIDERMAN

When title screen loads, hit joystick fire button.  At screen where it says:

        1) Play the game
        2) Spidey Take 0
        3) Quit the game

Choose Spidey Take 0: click joystick button once.  Now hit the '2' key on
the keyboard (not the numeric pad).  Once in the game, play as normal, but
now when you start to lose health (indicated by a change in the picture of
Spiderman, on the right side of the screen), just hit the 'Help' key and 
suddenly all energy is back.
@endnode
@node "SPIDERTRONIC (Infogrames)"
SPIDERTRONIC (Infogrames)

SPIDERTRONIC (Infogrames):

Get a high score and enter "CHEAT" on the screen, press 'Return' and then
the fire button; the screen will go black and a prompt will appear:

 Last game level: GAME.LS0  (or GAME.LS0 )??
 
 New game level:
 
Type GAME.LS and the number of the level you want to play.  Press 'Return'
and then the fire button, and you start playing on the desired level.
