@node "SPINDIZZY WORLDS"
SPINDIZZY WORLDS

There is actually a hidden level designer in Spindizzy.  Load up the game as
usual and select a cluster of planets to view it close up.  Now type in
"Edit" (in mixed case as shown) and a disclaimer screen will appear.  If you
agree to the disclaimer, some brief instructions will appear.  Press the
joystick button to return to the planet cluster and press the jopystick
button again to play.  There will not be any scenery there - you can now
create your own.
@endnode
