@node "SPITTIN' IMAGE"

SPITTIN' IMAGE

The game is easiest if fought in this order:

  1) Reagan, Pope
  2) Gorby, Pope
  3) Ayatollah, Pope
  4) Botha, Pope
  5) Margaret, Pope

Finally a couple of useful pointers: Keep close to your opponents, so they
can't hit you back.  Always move away from your opponents when their helpers
appear, and hit your opponents with your special move, when they are using
theirs.
@endnode
@node "SPY Vs SPY"
