@node "STORMLORD"
STORMLORD

First cheat:

On the credits screen type "DRAGONBRIDGE' (no spaces) and a scrolling
message should come across saying "You cheating swine".  In-game, press the
'SPACE BAR' to pause and then press 'L' to skip the level.  Also another
cheat is: when the game starts to load, hold down the mouse button and the
joystick fire button and keep them held down until the game loads.  Then when
the game starts, pause it straight away and type "MNBVC".  This will give you
infinite time and lives.  If you pause the game and press 'L' you will
advance a level.

Another cheat: Could be for Atari ST?

As the game starts to load, hold down left mouse button and firebutton, and
keep them down until game loads.  Then when the game starts, pause it and
type "MNBVC" for infinite time and lives.  Pause the game and press 'L' to
skip to the next level.
@endnode
