@node "STRIDER"
STRIDER

Press 'F9' to pause the game.  Hold 'HELP', 'Left Shift', and '1' on the main
keyboard.  Let go of all three, and press 'F10' to restart the game.

From now on the following keys are activated:

'1' - '5' (main keyboard) = Warp to corresponding level
'F1' - 'F4'               = Warp to section 1-4 in current level

If you are almost dead, just use the 'F1' - 'F4' keys (depending on how far
you are) for renewed strength!
@endnode
@node "STRIDER II"
STRIDER II

