                61:     ANJAMAUS
                66:     ODIN HOL IHN
                71:     SPERMINATOR
                76:     TACH NANA
                81:     YOU SEXY MF
@endnode
@node "SWIBBLE DRIBBLE 2"
SWIBBLE DRIBBLE 2

When you get to the purple dragon, type "DIE" and he will drop a purple key.
Take the key to Marvo and he will give you a cheat mode in return.
        
Typing: "BLOOD" makes Mortal Kombat-style blood fly out of your enemies.
        
Typing: "SUN" makes the sun wink at you.
        
Typing: "WHAT A CROC" makes Dibble shout, when you do something dumb.
@endnode                
@node "SWITCHBLADE"
SWITCHBLADE

On the Hi score table enter "POOKY" and hold down either the '1', '2', '3',
'4', or '5' keys and click on "END" to exit.  Continue clicking through the
opening screens while still holding down the selected key.  This will allow
you to begin the game at the selected level.
@endnode
@node "SWITCHBLADE II"
SWITCHBLADE II

On the title screen type in "LEVEL" followed by the number of the level you
want to start on.

You can also type in "CHROME" to enter a hidden sub-game.  For instance, type
"LEVEL3" to start on level 3.

The actual level codes to CHROME are as follows:

 1 - No Code    5 - CLOUD      9 - PAPER       13 - APPLE      17 - AUDIO
 2 - TRUTH      6 - MOUSE      10- EARTH       14 - JUICE      18 - LOGIC
 3 - JELLY      7 - HUMAN      11- SPACE       15 - CHESS      19 - TITLE
 4 - STORY      8 - FLOOR      12- GENAM       16 - WORLD      20 - VENUS
@endnode 
@node "SWIV"
SWIV

In-game press 'P' to pause the game and type "NCC-1701" (The '-' symbol
refers to the one on the main keyboard NOT the numeric keypad), then press
'N' and the screen will flash.  Press 'P' again to unpause and from there on
both players will now have infinite lives. 

After defeating a Goosecopter, fire continously at one of the tokens.  After
32 hits, it will turn into a star, which when collected will yield
mega-powerful six-way fire.  Just be careful not to hit the token again
before collecting it, or it will revert back to the one of the ordinary
power-up tokens.
@endnode
@node "SWORD OF SODAN"
SWORD OF SODAN

Type "NANCY" on hi score table for infinite lives.  Pressing 'Return' while
playing advances you a level.

Once loaded, select the hero, then lose all lives on the first screen.  Now
select the "HEROINE", and you should have infinite players.

If you type "RAD" in the high score table and play another game you will have
infinite lives.

Play the game, and get yourself killed, but ensure you get on the high score
table and enter your name.  Now start the game again, press fire so you can
move about.  Stand still (preferably no where near the guards!) and type
"DISCOVERYSOFTWARE" and press 'RETURN' (you should see a message on screen).
You will now have infinite lives and go on to the next level.  Now when you
press 'RETURN' at any time during play you will automatically go to the next
level.
@endnode
@node "SYNDICATE"
SYNDICATE

For extra cash name your company "ROB A BANK" and you will be rewarded with
1,000,000 credits.

For extra cash and all the weapons and modifiers already researched then name
your company "COOPER TEAM".

Type "WATCH THE CLOCK" to alter the game's timer so that missions that
normally last 17 hours will be extended to several days, thus giving you more
time to complete a mission.

Type "NUK THEM" to start in any country.
Type "OWN THEM" to own all the countries.
Type "MARKS TEAM" for the best team with loads of cyborgs and all researched.
@endnode  
